         <abstract>
            <p>When surveying the many methods currently employed in MT evaluation, it is not immediately obvious that the methods used serve to increase the knowledge of the properties being measured. This report describes a constructive machine translation evaluation method, aimed at addressing this issue.</p>
         </abstract>
